  "body": "\n\n<div class=\"obch-outer\">\n<div class=\"obch-inner\">\n<div class=\"obch-left\">\n<div class=\"obch-eyebrow obch-rev\"><div class=\"obch-ey-dot\"></div><span class=\"obch-ey-txt\">Brand Collaboration</span></div>\n<h1 class=\"obch-h1 obch-rev obch-d1\">Showcase Your Brand to<br/><em class=\"obch-h1-em\">50,000+ Construction</em><br/>Professionals across India</h1>\n<p class=\"obch-sub obch-rev obch-d1\">Promote your products and services directly to the decision-makers who plan, procure, and run construction projects every day.</p>\n<div class=\"obch-bullets obch-rev obch-d2\">\n<div class=\"obch-bullet\"><div class=\"obch-check\"><svg class=\"obch-check-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"obch-bullet-txt\">Builders and Developers</span></div>\n<div class=\"obch-bullet\"><div class=\"obch-check\"><svg class=\"obch-check-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"obch-bullet-txt\">Contractors and Subcontractors</span></div>\n<div class=\"obch-bullet\"><div class=\"obch-check\"><svg class=\"obch-check-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"obch-bullet-txt\">Interior Designers and Design Studios</span></div>\n<div class=\"obch-bullet\"><div class=\"obch-check\"><svg class=\"obch-check-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"obch-bullet-txt\">Project Managers and Site Engineers</span></div>\n<div class=\"obch-bullet\"><div class=\"obch-check\"><svg class=\"obch-check-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"obch-bullet-txt\">Purchase and Procurement Heads</span></div>\n<div class=\"obch-bullet\"><div class=\"obch-check\"><svg class=\"obch-check-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"obch-bullet-txt\">Construction Companies from MSME to Enterprise</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"obch-stats obch-rev obch-d3\">\n<div class=\"obch-stat\"><div class=\"obch-stat-n\">50,000+</div><div class=\"obch-stat-l\">Active professionals</div></div>\n<div class=\"obch-stat\"><div class=\"obch-stat-n\">500+</div><div class=\"obch-stat-l\">Construction companies</div></div>\n<div class=\"obch-stat\"><div class=\"obch-stat-n\">2</div><div class=\"obch-stat-l\">Markets — India and Gulf</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"obch-form-card obch-rev-r\">\n<div class=\"obch-form-title\">Get in Touch</div>\n<p class=\"obch-form-sub\">Tell us about your brand and we will share the collaboration options that fit your goals.</p>\n<div class=\"obch-form-divider\"></div>\n<div class=\"obch-form-wrap\"><div class=\"fluentform ff-default fluentform_wrapper_10 ffs_custom_wrap\"><div class=\"ff-errors-in-stack ff_form_instance_10_3 ff-form-loading_errors ff_form_instance_10_3_errors\" id=\"fluentform_10_errors\"></div></div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"obch-trust\"><span class=\"obch-trust-stars\">★★★★★</span><span class=\"obch-trust-txt\">Trusted by 10,000+ construction companies</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"obcf-outer\">\n<div class=\"obcf-inner\">\n<div class=\"obcf-head obcf-rev\">\n<div class=\"obcf-eyebrow\"><div class=\"obcf-ey-dot\"></div><span class=\"obcf-ey-txt\">Ad Formats</span></div>\n<h2 class=\"obcf-h2\">Four ways to reach <em class=\"obcf-h2-em\">construction professionals</em></h2>\n<p class=\"obcf-head-sub\">Every format is built around how construction teams actually use SiteFlow — on site, in the office, and during procurement.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"obcf-grid\">\n Card 1: Spotlight Banners — COLOR: icon bg/stroke rose; tags rose \n<div class=\"obcf-card obcf-card-1 obcf-rev obcf-d1\">\n<div class=\"obcf-icon\" style=\"background:#fff0f3!important;\"><svg class=\"obcf-icon-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><rect height=\"12\" rx=\"2\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" width=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\"></rect><path d=\"M8 20h8M12 16v4\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path><path d=\"M7 9h5M7 12h3\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></path><circle cx=\"16\" cy=\"10\" fill=\"#d30d50\" opacity=\"0.3\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div>\n<h3 class=\"obcf-name\">Spotlight Banners</h3>\n<p class=\"obcf-desc\">High-visibility banner placements inside the SiteFlow web and mobile app — seen by project managers and site engineers during active project work.</p>\n<div class=\"obcf-card-divider\"></div>\n<div class=\"obcf-best\"><span class=\"obcf-best-lbl\">Best for</span><div class=\"obcf-tags\"><span class=\"obcf-tag\" style=\"background:#fff0f3!important;color:#a50c3c!important;\">Material brands</span><span class=\"obcf-tag\" style=\"background:#fff0f3!important;color:#a50c3c!important;\">Equipment companies</span><span class=\"obcf-tag\" style=\"background:#fff0f3!important;color:#a50c3c!important;\">Software tools</span></div></div>\n</div>\n Card 2: RFQ Promotions — blue kept \n<div class=\"obcf-card obcf-card-2 obcf-rev obcf-d2\">\n<div class=\"obcf-icon\" style=\"background:#dbeafe!important;\"><svg class=\"obcf-icon-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M9 17H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3\" stroke=\"#1d4ed8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path><path d=\"M13 21l2-2m0 0l4-4m-4 4l4 4m-4-4h6\" stroke=\"#1d4ed8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path><path d=\"M7 8h6M7 12h4\" stroke=\"#1d4ed8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></path></svg></div>\n<h3 class=\"obcf-name\">RFQ Promotions</h3>\n<p class=\"obcf-desc\">Appear at the moment procurement teams send or receive RFQs inside SiteFlow. Your brand reaches purchase heads when they are actively buying materials or hiring vendors.</p>\n<div class=\"obcf-card-divider\"></div>\n<div class=\"obcf-best\"><span class=\"obcf-best-lbl\">Best for</span><div class=\"obcf-tags\"><span class=\"obcf-tag\" style=\"background:#dbeafe!important;color:#1d4ed8!important;\">Suppliers and distributors</span><span class=\"obcf-tag\" style=\"background:#dbeafe!important;color:#1d4ed8!important;\">Rental companies</span></div></div>\n</div>\n Card 3: Service Listings — green kept \n<div class=\"obcf-card obcf-card-3 obcf-rev obcf-d3\">\n<div class=\"obcf-icon\" style=\"background:#d1fae5!important;\"><svg class=\"obcf-icon-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M9 5H7a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path><rect height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" width=\"6\" x=\"9\" y=\"3\"></rect><path d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path></svg></div>\n<h3 class=\"obcf-name\">Service Listings</h3>\n<p class=\"obcf-desc\">A dedicated listing for your company inside SiteFlow’s vendor and service directory — searchable by contractors and builders when they need your category of product or service.</p>\n<div class=\"obcf-card-divider\"></div>\n<div class=\"obcf-best\"><span class=\"obcf-best-lbl\">Best for</span><div class=\"obcf-tags\"><span class=\"obcf-tag\" style=\"background:#d1fae5!important;color:#059669!important;\">Labour providers</span><span class=\"obcf-tag\" style=\"background:#d1fae5!important;color:#059669!important;\">Finance services</span><span class=\"obcf-tag\" style=\"background:#d1fae5!important;color:#059669!important;\">Training institutes</span></div></div>\n</div>\n Card 4: Lead Gen Cards — amber kept \n<div class=\"obcf-card obcf-card-4 obcf-rev obcf-d4\">\n<div class=\"obcf-icon\" style=\"background:#fef3c7!important;\"><svg class=\"obcf-icon-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\" stroke=\"#b45309\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\" stroke=\"#b45309\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></circle><path d=\"M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\" stroke=\"#b45309\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path></svg></div>\n<h3 class=\"obcf-name\">Lead Gen Cards</h3>\n<p class=\"obcf-desc\">Contextual cards that appear at the right moment in a user’s workflow — with a direct inquiry form so interested contractors and builders can reach you in one tap.</p>\n<div class=\"obcf-card-divider\"></div>\n<div class=\"obcf-best\"><span class=\"obcf-best-lbl\">Best for</span><div class=\"obcf-tags\"><span class=\"obcf-tag\" style=\"background:#fef3c7!important;color:#b45309!important;\">Real estate developers</span><span class=\"obcf-tag\" style=\"background:#fef3c7!important;color:#b45309!important;\">Insurance services</span></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"obcf-strip obcf-rev\">\n<p class=\"obcf-strip-txt\">Not sure which format fits? <span>We will recommend the right one</span> after a short call.</p>\n<a class=\"obcf-strip-btn\" href=\"#fluentform_10\">Talk to us<svg class=\"obcf-strip-btn-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n FAQ \n<div class=\"obcfq-outer\">\n<div class=\"obcfq-inner\">\n<div class=\"obcfq-head obcfq-rev\">\n<div class=\"obcfq-eyebrow\"><div class=\"obcfq-ey-dot\"></div><span class=\"obcfq-ey-txt\">FAQ</span></div>\n<h2 class=\"obcfq-h2\">Questions about advertising with SiteFlow</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"obcfq-grid\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/FAQPage\">\n<div class=\"obcfq-item obcfq-rev\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"obcfq-btn\" onclick=\"obcfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"obcfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Who will actually see my brand on SiteFlow?</span><span class=\"obcfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"obcfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"obcfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Your brand reaches the people actively running construction projects — project managers, site engineers, procurement heads, builders, and contractors. These are working professionals using SiteFlow daily to track labour, manage materials, run billing, and report to clients. The audience is not a general consumer base — it is a focused group of construction decision-makers across India and the Gulf.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"obcfq-item obcfq-rev obcfq-d1\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"obcfq-btn\" onclick=\"obcfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"obcfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">What is the minimum commitment to get started?</span><span class=\"obcfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"obcfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"obcfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">There is no fixed minimum — collaboration options are scoped based on your goals, budget, and the format that fits best. We recommend starting with a short introductory call where we understand what you are trying to achieve. From there we propose a plan that is sized to your needs, whether that is a one-month trial or a longer campaign.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"obcfq-item obcfq-rev\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"obcfq-btn\" onclick=\"obcfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"obcfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Which industries or brand types are a good fit?</span><span class=\"obcfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"obcfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"obcfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">The best fit brands are those whose products or services are relevant to active construction work. This includes construction material suppliers, cement and steel brands, equipment and machinery companies, equipment rental firms, labour and workforce providers, construction finance and insurance services, real estate developers, and training or certification institutes for site professionals.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"obcfq-item obcfq-rev obcfq-d1\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"obcfq-btn\" onclick=\"obcfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"obcfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">How is performance tracked and reported?</span><span class=\"obcfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"obcfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"obcfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">We share campaign reports covering impressions, clicks, and leads generated — depending on the format you choose. For Lead Gen Cards and RFQ Promotions, you receive direct lead data with contact details. For Spotlight Banners and Service Listings, we provide reach and engagement metrics. Reports are shared on an agreed cadence — weekly or monthly.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"obcfq-item obcfq-rev\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"obcfq-btn\" onclick=\"obcfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"obcfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Do you offer exclusivity for a category?</span><span class=\"obcfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"obcfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"obcfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Yes. For certain formats we offer category exclusivity — meaning no direct competitor brand appears in the same placement during your campaign period. This is available on a first-come basis and depends on the format and geography. Mention this in your inquiry and we will confirm availability for your specific category.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"obcfq-item obcfq-rev obcfq-d1\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"obcfq-btn\" onclick=\"obcfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"obcfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Can I target specific geographies or project types?</span><span class=\"obcfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"obcfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"obcfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Yes. SiteFlow has an active user base across India and the Gulf — and within India across multiple cities and states. We can discuss geographic targeting based on where your brand operates or distributes. Some formats also allow filtering by project type, such as residential, commercial, or infrastructure, depending on the campaign.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"obcfq-item obcfq-rev\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"obcfq-btn\" onclick=\"obcfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"obcfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">How quickly can a campaign go live?</span><span class=\"obcfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"obcfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"obcfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Most campaigns can go live within 5 to 7 business days after the brief is confirmed and creatives are approved. Service Listings can be live within 2 to 3 days. If you have an upcoming product launch or seasonal campaign, mention your timeline in the form and we will prioritise accordingly.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"obcfq-item obcfq-rev obcfq-d1\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"obcfq-btn\" onclick=\"obcfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"obcfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">What happens after I submit the form?</span><span class=\"obcfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"obcfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"obcfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Our partnerships team reviews your inquiry and responds within one business day. We then schedule a brief 20-minute call to understand your brand, target audience, and campaign goals. After the call we share a tailored collaboration proposal with format recommendations, reach estimates, and pricing. There is no pressure to commit immediately.</p></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n CTA \n<div class=\"obcfc-outer\">\n<div class=\"obcfc-inner obcfq-rev obcfq-d1\">\n<div class=\"obcfc-eyebrow\"><div class=\"obcfc-ey-dot\"></div><span class=\"obcfc-ey-txt\">Start advertising</span></div>\n<h2 class=\"obcfc-h2\">Your brand. Their next<br/><em class=\"obcfc-h2-em\">construction project.</em></h2>\n<p class=\"obcfc-sub\">50,000 plus construction professionals use SiteFlow every day. A 20-minute call is all it takes to put your brand in front of the right ones.</p>\n<div class=\"obcfc-btns\">\n<a class=\"obcfc-btn-primary\" href=\"#fluentform_10\">Get in Touch</a>\n<a class=\"obcfc-btn-outline\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/customers/\">See Who Uses SiteFlow</a>\n</div>\n<p class=\"obcfc-fine\">No commitment required  ·  Response within 1 business day  ·  Category exclusivity available</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n"
}